nodes.text: Sector 33G. 925 was a subsector located in the Lothal sector of the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories. During the rule of the Galactic Empire, the Lothal sector and its subsectors, including Sector 33G. 925, was ruled by the Empire and controlled by Governor Arihnda Pryce, a human female from the planet Lothal, and Moff Stattata.
